{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十二回\"恩仇问苍天\"。铁中棠身受霹雳火相救之恩与信任之情，恩仇交错、内心矛盾。海大少看出霹雳火将铁中棠视为再生之子，提议收徒，铁中棠以不愿辈分拘束为由婉拒，三人遂以知交酒友相处。船靠黄河岸边，舟子\"快船\"张三快口快船、骄傲有气概。欧阳兄弟鲜衣怒马沿河搜索蜂女舟踪迹，匆匆而过。三人在荒野遇锦衣大汉拦路伏桩，海大少以银票设局引诱，识破盗贼在前方做案，制服二人后捆缚。铁中棠判断欧阳兄弟正是盗贼目标，三人飞步赶往前方查看。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "确实有些奇怪。老夫自己也不知为何会如此待你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你心里奇怪，俺心里倒不奇怪。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "这种没头没脑的话，老夫一向听不懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "你不知为何如此对他，俺却知道。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "难道你能钻入老夫肚子里去么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "你这老儿，再如此胡言乱语，俺就……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "莫怪莫怪，且说来听听，对也不对。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "你这老儿肚里有几条肠子，俺都摸得清清楚楚了，焉有说不对之理。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "好，好，你若说对了，老夫定要好好请你……自然少不得要先痛饮三百杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "只因你这老儿，生平无子无女，好容易收了个徒儿，却又偏偏给别人偷跑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "而这少年的性命，却又是你亲手自阴间救回来的，常言道：'恩同再造，再生父母。'人家心里还不知怎样想，你这老儿不知不觉暗暗将别人当做你造出的儿子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "造出的儿子，好难听的话，你用字可以用得文雅些么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "字虽不雅，却是再恰当没有，一个五六十岁的孤老儿突然造了个儿子，自然要对他好的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，俺看你不如将他真的收为义子罢了，俺也好喝杯喜酒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你这老儿，除了喝酒还会想别的么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "你嘴里虽在骂俺，心里却实在感激得很，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "不错不错，老夫实在是有些感激的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "若要你真的称他为父，未免要折煞这老儿了，俺看你根骨颇佳，年纪又轻，正是学武的好材料，而这老儿也恰巧少了个徒弟，你不如拜他为师，倒是两全其美。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个……这个……武功在下早已练过。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是……但是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "还但是什么？这老儿外貌虽不佳，却是名震武林的霹雳堂第五代堂主，当今天下闻名的霹雳火，你若拜在他门下，便再也不会受人的气了。只是，他日你当了霹雳堂少主人，却万万不可忘了请俺痛饮几杯美酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位请恕在下不能拜他为师。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你莫非不知道霹雳堂在当今武林中的赫赫声名么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "在下自然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "既然知道，为何不肯，莫非……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "莫非嫌我霹雳堂三字，还辱没了你不成？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下焉有此意，只是……只是……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "只是为了什么，老夫倒想听听。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下与两位一见投缘，本待高攀两泣，做个知交酒友，若要在下拜在你门下，在下立刻低了一辈，不但言行都要大受拘束，便是日后喝酒，也喝不痛快了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错不错。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有理有理，若换了老夫，实也不愿由别人的朋友，一下变作别人的徒弟。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此你虽少了个徒弟，却多了个酒友，妙极妙极……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫正急着喝酒，你为何靠在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_chuan_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "快船张三",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "前面水流太急，这船上载的人又已过多，到前面若是翻了船，各位便喝不成酒了，倒不如在这里靠岸，虽然慢些，但终究是有酒喝的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_zhou_zi",
      "text": "哎哟，好利的嘴，早知你如此利口，老夫又何苦花双倍银子，雇你的船？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_chuan_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "快船张三",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "黄河道上，谁不知'快船'张三，快口快船？若不雇我的船，这条水路谁走得动？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_zhou_zi",
      "text": "好，好好，能干的小伙子，纵然骄一些，老夫也不生气。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_chuan_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "快船张三",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "若不能干，也不敢在你老面前骄了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_zhou_zi",
      "text": "若不能干还要骄，老夫不将你一脚踢下河去才怪！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_zhou_zi",
      "text": "张三，你这小子虽然的确狂些，但俺瞧着也顺眼，先弄些银子去买酒吃，日后有事再来寻我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_chuan_zhang_san",
      "speaker_name": "快船张三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "他们瞧着我顺眼，我却瞧着你顺眼，他日若在黄河道上有什么事，只管来寻快船张三。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早知如此……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "马上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒怪了，偌大艘船，怎会突然不见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "又有人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老三莫心焦，说不定就在前面。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小伙子们哪里去？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些少年是谁？怎的如此无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "还有谁？自然便是那不知天多高、地多厚的欧阳兄弟，放着好日子不过，却定要去惹马蜂窝。幸好那艘蜂女舟已沉下，否则他们的乐子还大着哩，俺看在他们尊长面上，少不得又要多事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这批小伙子有钱闲着，又被色迷了心窍，若换了老夫，真不愿伸手去管这闲事了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实，欧阳世家本重声色，府上不乏丽人，俺真不懂他们为何偏偏定要来寻那些扎人的野蜂子？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "海老弟，这事你就不懂。常言道：家花不如野花香，他们见多了温柔美丽的多情女子，自然认为不够刺激，自然要寻些扎人的野花换换口味，而越是不易到手的货色，他们便越觉有趣。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "看不出你经验倒也丰富得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中似你这般不近女色的鲁男子，算来又有几个？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个不知事的瞎眼贼子，动手脚居然动到贼爷爷身上来了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位且莫惊动，待俺先在这厮身上取个乐子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三位若要赶路，请绕道走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "text": "好汉爷，咱们出来走道，身上并未曾带得银子。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "谁要你的银子，快走吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "text": "不要银子，来作甚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你耳朵聋了么？咱们只要你绕道而走，莫要再往前面这条路走就是了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "看来他这乐子取不成了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "text": "不瞒两位，俺身上委实带得有银子的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你有银子业好，快带着银子走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "text": "俺身上不但有银子，还有不少，两位好汉爷若是要，只管拿去就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "text": "两位要，只管拿去，在下绝对不敢反抗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_er",
      "text": "孙老二，这厮既然定要咱们动手，咱们倒也不愿辜负了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "孙老二",
      "listener": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "text": "但……但老爷子的话……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_er",
      "text": "这是他自己送上来的，不拿实在有些对不起人，反正只要不是咱们自己动手去抢，老爷子想必也不会怪咱们。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，果然是强盗，敢抢大爷们的银子，当真是瞎了眼了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "锦衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "我只当你是个痰迷心窍的半疯子，哪知你竟是成心惹事来了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，俺就是成心来砸你们锅的。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "躺下吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "孙老二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，你等着！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_er",
      "text": "好小子，竟敢出口伤人！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "你这乐子未免弄得太刻薄了些！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "你当俺是在寻乐子的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "若不取乐为何苦苦逼人家来抢你的银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "错了错丁，这两人在此伏桩，定要我等改道，为的是什么？你莫非还猜不到？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "是了，必定是因为他伙伴在前面做案，不愿被外人惊散好事。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "他两人不愿来抢俺的银子，也不过只是因为上头有令，叫他们莫抢了小的，惊了大的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "不错不错，因小失大，便是笨贼了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "这些贼非但不笨，而且令出如山，显见得组织定必十分严密，瓢把子也定必有些来头。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "看不出你粗手粗脚，脑筋倒清楚得很。既是如此，你我快打前面看看，那究竟是什么来头。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_er",
      "text": "念在你们先还客气，且饶你一命。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "什么是了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "text": "欧阳兄弟鲜衣怒马，驰聘江滨，必定惹人眼红，我若要上线开扒，也必要抢他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_da_shao",
      "speaker_name": "海大少",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "speaker_name": "霹雳火",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "小伙子，你追得上老夫么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_pi_li_huo",
      "text": "在下轻功不佳，万万追不上的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 337
    }
